## Beton-AI Design System Rules (shadcn/ui + Tailwind)

This repository implements a shadcn/ui-based design system with Tailwind CSS tokens and Radix primitives. Use this document to reliably translate Figma designs (for an open-source lead enrichment app, Clay.com alternative) into production code.

### Token Definitions

- **Where**
  - CSS custom properties define tokens in `frontend/src/app/globals.css` under `:root` and `.dark`.
  - Tailwind maps design tokens to utilities in `frontend/tailwind.config.js` via `hsl(var(--token))`.

