- **Location**
  - shadcn/ui components live in `frontend/src/components/ui` (e.g., `button.tsx`, `dialog.tsx`, `dropdown-menu.tsx`, etc.).

- **Architecture**
  - Components wrap Radix primitives and style with Tailwind. Variants use `class-variance-authority (cva)` and `cn` utility.
